signatureAbility.signatureDescription: Quarterbacks with generational arms have the power to stretch any defense to its breaking point. When they enter the zone, their maximum throw distance is increased by 15+ yards.
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all throws while running outside the pocket (except on high/low throws).
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all unpressured throws inside the red zone (except on high/low throws).
Passers with this ability are faster and more responsive to user input while scrambling behind the line of scrimmage.
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all cross-body throws (except on high/low throws).
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all deep throws while their feet are set (except on high/low throws).
Defenders with this ability are rarely faked out by ballcarrier moves (and cannot be faked out when user-controlled).
Defenders with this ability have higher chance to catch uncontested interceptions, and they have unlimited stamina on the return (until using a special move or breaking a tackle).
Defenders with this ability are rarely faked out by ballcarrier moves (and cannot be faked out when user-controlled).
Defenders with this ability don't allow broken tackles when hit-sticking ballcarriers - regardless of the runner's size or power.
Aggressive receivers overpower defenders and attack the football. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their success rate on aggressive catches against single coverage.
True legendary receivers make the impossible possible. When they enter the zone, they have greatly increased success rate on aggressive catches of 50+ yards regardless of coverage.
Receivers with this ability run sharper routes and catch more consistently while running post and corner routes.
Receivers with this ability run sharper routes and catch more consistently while running streak routes.
Players with this ability have an increased chance to catch passes that have been tipped into the air.
